{"tid":1342661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家同我記住我地既目標係咩！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:12:07.000Z","uid":204565,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc2cef56dae4be150990182b77fa56d1809369d","tid":1342661,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:49:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽日圍唔圍元朗?</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">圍！！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地要唔要為上環既手足拎返個公道?</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要！！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地兩邊戰線都唔可以比佢停！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好淨係比佢地班垃圾用黑社會就令到我地既目標轉！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地既目標由此至終都係要推反中共！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求缺一不可！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究黑警責任！！<br />\n釋放義士！！！<br />\n撤回暴動定性！！<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會！！！<br />\n建立雙普選！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！！<br />\n時代革命！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9e1037d278050768f673634e146b0a9ae5951696","tid":1342661,"uid":204565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:50:59.000Z","msg":"聽日出係好急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地知道如果比啲黑社會再亂黎只會令到更多人受傷同死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" c